  "markup": "Dr. Christopher Carraway of LTU, interviews Randolph Merrick, MD,Treasurer of NAALT and Family Medicine Physician at the NAALT/WALT joint meeting in Washington, DC, September 2014 as he reviews the diseases and conditions he has been utilizing LLLT in his daily private practice.\u0026nbsp; Dr. Merrick also updates us on where he sees Low Level Laser Therapy heading in the very near future in general medicine.\u0026nbsp;"
}]]></Value>
